worms.model.programs

Class ParseOutcome<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • worms.model.programs.ParseOutcome<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ParseOutcome.Failure, ParseOutcome.Success

    public abstract class ParseOutcome<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the outcome of parsing a program. The outcome can denote success or failure. Depending on the outcome, the result may have a different type T.
